---
// Founder.astro — Sticky Image & Scrolling Content
---

<section class="bg-peach/25 py-0 relative">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row relative w-full items-start">
        <!-- Scrolling Text Panel (Left) -->
        <div
            class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-24 md:py-0 md:min-h-[150vh] order-2 md:order-1 z-10 bg-peach/25"
        >
            <div
                class="founder-text-content md:sticky md:top-1/2 md:-translate-y-1/2"
            >
                <span
                    class="text-[12px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-main/50 mb-6 block"
                >
                    La Especialista
                </span>
                <h2
                    class="font-serif text-[40px] md:text-[60px] tracking-tight text-main leading-[1.1] mb-4"
                >
                    Natalia<br /><span class="italic text-base/80"
                        >Regalado</span
                    >
                </h2>
                <p class="font-serif text-[18px] text-accent-luxury mb-8">
                    Fundadora &nbsp;|&nbsp; Psicología (URV), Masajista (IMPE0110) & AFDA0210
                </p>
                <div class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-main/20 mb-8"></div>
                <p
                    class="text-[16px] md:text-[18px] text-main/70 leading-[1.7] mb-6 max-w-md"
                >
                    Habiendo superado ella misma el acoso (bullying), la depresión severa, la obesidad y los problemas de socialización, Natalia comprende íntimamente lo que significa el estancamiento vital y el rechazo hacia el propio cuerpo.
                </p>
                <p
                    class="text-[16px] md:text-[18px] text-main/70 leading-[1.7] mb-10 max-w-md"
                >
                    Mediante su formación —Grado en Psicología (URV), titulación oficial en Masaje (IMPE0110) y Acondicionamiento Físico (AFDA0210)— unida a múltiples cursos complementarios, ha diseñado un método donde el rigor científico se abraza a la pura empatía vivencial.
                </p>
                <a href="#" class="pill-btn pill-btn--outline w-fit">
                    <span class="text-accent-luxury text-[14px]">✳︎</span>
                    Nuestra filosofía
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sticky Image Panel (Right) -->
        <div
            class="founder-image-pin w-full md:w-1/2 sticky top-0 h-[60vh] md:h-screen order-1 md:order-2 overflow-hidden bg-main border-l border-main/10 relative"
        >
            <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
                <img
                    src="/founder_portrait.png"
                    alt="Natalia Regalado — Fundadora"
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top opacity-90 scale-105"
                    loading="lazy"
                />
            </div>
            <!-- Overlay to make it feel more editorial -->
            <div
                class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-main/60 via-transparent to-transparent"
            >
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<script>
    import { gsap } from "gsap";
    import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger";

    document.addEventListener("astro:page-load", () => {
        gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

        // Image Parallax on Sticky
        gsap.to(".founder-image-pin img", {
            yPercent: 8,
            ease: "none",
            scrollTrigger: {
                trigger: ".founder-image-pin",
                start: "top bottom",
                end: "bottom top",
                scrub: true,
            },
        });

        // Text reveal stagger
        gsap.from(".founder-text-content > *", {
            y: 40,
            opacity: 0,
            duration: 1,
            stagger: 0.15,
            ease: "power3.out",
            scrollTrigger: {
                trigger: ".founder-text-content",
                start: "top 80%",
            },
        });
    });
</script>
